                            <comment id="13653595" author="elyograg" created="Fri, 10 May 2013 07:00:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&quot;Fix Version/s&quot; includes 4.3.1, as this will probably be a small and safe fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13653599" author="elyograg" created="Fri, 10 May 2013 07:01:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve assigned the issue to myself, but anyone who wants it is free to take it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13654757" author="elyograg" created="Fri, 10 May 2013 19:23:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch against trunk that sends logging from zkCLI at INFO to stderr, which is what it did before the log4j change.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This also fixes a bug that prevented zkcli.bat from working on windows.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13654908" author="shalinmangar" created="Fri, 10 May 2013 21:57:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13654922" author="elyograg" created="Fri, 10 May 2013 22:13:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;New patch with cosmetic formatting updates, a CHANGES.txt entry in the 4.3.1 section, and svn eol-style on the new properties file.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I would appreciate a quick review and a note from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=shalin&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;shalin&quot;&gt;shalin&lt;/a&gt; about whether it is OK to include in 4.3.1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13654931" author="shalinmangar" created="Fri, 10 May 2013 22:20:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I should have clarified. My +1 was for including it in 4.3.1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Having no logs is annoying but zkcli not working on windows is more serious and should also be mentioned in the change log.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13654938" author="elyograg" created="Fri, 10 May 2013 22:28:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated CHANGES.txt to include note about the fix for Windows.  This is the version that I am committing and backporting.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
